Class GovernanceServiceConfigurationEvent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class GovernanceServiceConfigurationEvent
extends GovernanceEngineEvent
    GovernanceServiceConfigurationEvent is used to inform a governance server that the configuration of one of the governance services within one of its governance engines has changed.
